data.description: Price Reduction for quick sale.  Motivated Seller.  You don't want to miss seeing this move in ready, well taken care of home.  Home has 3 bedrooms, 1 1/2 bathrooms, 2 living spaces, office area, dining room, inside laundry, and attached 1 car garage with new garage door opener.  The roof was replaced in 2016, HVAC serviced regularly, sewer pipe replaced, oven never used, new kitchen faucet, new plumbing lines under sink, updated windows, fresh caulk on exterior, power smart electric meter, electrician came and fixed 3 outlets.  There are original hard wood floors throughout home if ever decide to remove carpet.   Large back yard.   Washer, dryer, and refrigerator to stay with the home.
